{
  "stem": "8916.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So she set the teapot down, and just by instinct, just crawled up into this crawl space and crawled in with us, left the teapot on the ground.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the Germans were running around, and they're yelling.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They hauled the woman, the mother of those two children, out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was a lot of screaming and yelling.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we lay there for some time while this was going on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then when nightfall came, things began to quiet down.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We could just hear sporadic shootings and yelling.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then finally, it got quiet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we just laid there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We were afraid to come out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We didn't know what was happening.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And so eventually, the following day, somebody did come, came into the yard.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And-- and said, OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It's ready.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You know, you can come out now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It's safe.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But by that time, we had too many tricks and too many deceptions, so we decided that maybe we shouldn't come out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So we stayed there until somebody came the following day and called us by name.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "My father had sent someone and tried-- he didn't know whether we survived or not.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But he thought if by some chance if we did, if he called us by name, maybe we would come out.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we did.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
